{"tid":111713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超大波)「客戶都很體貼」 25歲人妻當全裸家政婦賺奶粉錢","createTime":"2017-02-07T14:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T08:26:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0be5b2cccf3453ec690e167286315d38268f58","tid":111713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/07/99/3147246.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F99%2F3147246.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=b4ab796f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠徵裸女當家事服務員！英國利物浦一名已婚、育有一女的媽媽妮可絲（Emily Nikols）為賺女兒奶粉錢，貼補家用，當起全裸家事員，服務崇尚裸體的客戶，每小時可賺45英鎊（約新台幣2200元）。<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，25歲的妮可絲為了賺取奶粉錢，在「裸體清潔員」（Naturist Cleaners）公司服務，對於外界異樣眼光，妮可絲堅持她的客戶都非常「體貼」、「好相處」，讓她在工作感到十分自在。<br />\n<br />\n妮可絲表示，裸體打掃沒什麼大不了，唯一讓她比較擔心的是老公想法，「原先他擔心我的安全，但他相信我會為自己的安全負責，何況我也不是性玩物，不是要去賣肉！身材不好絕對不是問題。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，該公司在全英國雇用80名男女裸體家事員，最低每小時向顧客酌收45英鎊（約新台幣2200元），且與顧客約定不得騷擾家事員，也不能做出任何性暗示。家事員因全裸打掃，也不能做太粗重的工作，或使用太刺激的清潔劑。<br />\n<br />\n國外網友感到訝異，「我不相信裸體幫人打掃，不會讓人想歪」、「某些詭異的人出現在詭異的世界」，也有人表示妮可絲沒做錯任何事，「有需求就供給，何況她也是踏實的在賺錢，祝福她。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/2269313?from=udn-hotnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F2269313%3Ffrom%3Dudn-hotnews_ch2&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=526b2d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/2269313?from=udn-hotnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"00be2682dafd8cd695e57810d208dfea522eeadd","tid":111713,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"波？"},{"pid":"69382261fc5b66aae227d1878233321d03d40136","tid":111713,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"有裸男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e88fd940c7799953edbbfa3b4bc66e6f1944957","tid":111713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8bbdc959c3b5d92b8fbcf1d19723d21a2060d4","tid":111713,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係肥婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f0d635426c28b88a38500a734b230b42cfd096","tid":111713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}